	**************************************************
	*						 *
	*	       1.0 SERIES NEWS			 *
	*						 *
	**************************************************


                CHANGES IN R VERSION 1.0.1


BUG FIXES

    o   Fix for tcltk global namespace leakage patch. Thanks for
	breaking code that had worked for over a decade to correct
	a corner-case nonissue (allowing '<-' to be redefined).
        <https://bugs.r-project.org/bugzilla3/show_bug.cgi?id=15970>


                CHANGES IN R VERSION 1.0.0


SIGNIFICANT USER-VISIBLE CHANGES

    o   Dropped compatibility for anything less than R-2.15 as
        no longer able to test against previous versions of R.

NEW FEATURES

    o   Updated package dependency/namespace issues to current
        standard (for R-3.x compatibility). No code changes.

    o   Added SVN revision information to many of the package files.

    o   Added COPYRIGHTS file.


	**************************************************
	*						 *
	*	       0.8 SERIES NEWS			 *
	*						 *
	**************************************************


                CHANGES IN R VERSION 0.8.3


BUG FIXES

    o   Updated .onLoad() method to remove corner-case package
        loading patch (for R-2.14 compatibility).


		CHANGES IN R VERSION 0.8.2


NEW FEATURES

    o	Added tkimage.delete() method (missing from tcltk).



		CHANGES IN R VERSION 0.8.1


BUG FIXES

    o	Loading of Tk option database with package-required values
	was not occurring on Windows.


		CHANGES IN R VERSION 0.8.0


NEW FEATURES

    o	Added tkloadappdefaults() method to provide a high-level
	means of loading the Tk option database from
	application-default files.


	**************************************************
	*						 *
	*	       0.7 SERIES NEWS			 *
