	**************************************************


		CHANGES IN R VERSION 0.7.1


NEW FEATURES

    o	Added tclinfo.hostname() method.


		CHANGES IN R VERSION 0.7.0


NEW FEATURES

    o	Initial release as a collection of packaged routines.

